Package org.rogatio.circlead.main

Class AtlassianPojoCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rogatio.circlead.main.AtlassianPojoCreator
  • public class AtlassianPojoCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class AtlassianPojoCreator creates POJO-Classes from found response to atlassian-server. All sources are saved in folder "lib" in classpath.
    Author:
    Matthias Wegner

      • createAtlassianPojos

        public static void createAtlassianPojos​(java.lang.String jiraJQL,
                                        java.lang.String roleID,
                                        java.lang.String spaceID)
        Creates the atlassian pojos.
        Parameters:
        jiraJQL - the jira JQL. Must find a representative set of issues. Query must return more than one result
        roleID - the role ID. Id of a role in confluence. Page must have at lease two historic page versions
        spaceID - the space ID. Id of the space. If null 'CIRCLEAD' is set as default
